{"tid":1378968,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中發展到現時已進入囚徒困境","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:54.000Z","uid":245320,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56ba94adc307a942d75fe35979ed10574123d5a4","tid":1378968,"uid":245320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"首先簡單解釋下咩叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">囚徒困境</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">囚徒困境</span></span></strong>是博弈論入面指非零和博弈既困局中對<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人理性既最佳選擇</span></span></strong>會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">引致團體全盤皆輸既結果</span></span></strong>，而反送中運動入面，反送中同親中陣營既對立係屬於零和博弈，基本上唔係贏就係輸曬，我唔打算詳細講。<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係反送中陣營入面既困境，反送中陣營主要分為<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「前線」</span></strong></span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「和理非」</span></strong></span>；以我既理解其中<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「和理非」</span></strong></span>至少又分兩大類，為免混淆，我會以七一遊行正義道向左走向右走黎分。<br />\n<br />\n向左走（下稱<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「泛民」</strong></span>）<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不分化，我知用詞未必準確，但暫時未諗到更好</ins></span></span>：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">遊行完民陣路線就會返屋企，可能係帶住老人家細路，冇心理準備承受抗爭後果既一群</span><br />\n向右走（下稱<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「和理非」</strong></span>）：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">會去支持前線示威者，但唔會去到前線，主要係後援，物資人鏈，充撐人數增加士氣等</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">（狀況甲）反送中運動成功既結果，係實現五大訴求，撤回送中條例，收回「暴動」定性，整治黑警，釋放義士，實施真普選</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（狀況乙）反送中運動失敗既結果，係全面支那化，全民人面識別監控，網絡實名制，進入巨型數位監獄時代，甚至進入新彊式再教育營，係永久性失去人權同自由</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">（狀況丙）黑警濫權濫捕同實行白／紅色恐怖，係對任何抗爭人士都可能會有嚴重法律效果(非法集結罪最高5年，暴動罪最高10年等...），係物理上直接失去</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和平集會遊行示威係直接表達民意既最好方法，但由於相信黑警唔會再批對於大部份<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「泛民」</span></strong>，甚至<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「和理非」</span></strong>黎講係「免死金牌」既不反對通知書，所有抗爭行為都有可能進入<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>（狀況丙）</strong></span>，對大部份人黎講既個人理性既最佳選擇係避免<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">（狀況丙）</span></strong>，返去飲飲食食返工搵錢呢種港豬模式唔再抗爭而變相出賣<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「前線」</strong></span>，而結果就係引致團體全盤皆輸進入<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（狀況乙）</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n未來<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警政府</span></strong></span>只會變本加厲，愈來愈<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無法無天</span></strong></span>，會不斷<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挑戰香港人既信心</span></span></strong>，但其實<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">囚徒困境</span></span></strong>既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">破局</span></strong>[/size=6]方法<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好簡單</span></span></strong>，係給予其他人<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">[size=5]信任[/size=6]</span></strong>，我深信抗爭形式會<strong>[size=5]<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">上善若水</span></span></strong>，會出現唔輕易進入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">（狀況丙）</span></strong>既模式，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不撤不散[/size=6]</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[size=5]<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛死全家</span></div></span></strong>"},{"pid":"84d2ae24378d9d711c50927c185eb6d78ae003c6","tid":1378968,"uid":245320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"Sor for 1999"},{"pid":"153f5e8083e4705ed1ee30a5e9dad397c577577e","tid":1378968,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0